descript.abstract: [Metadata] Description: Streets for the island of Oahu only as of May, 2021.Source: Honolulu Land Information System (HOLIS), C&C of Honolulu, May 20, 2022.For additional information, please refer to complete metadata at https://files.hawaii.gov/dbedt/op/gis/data/streets_oah.pdf or contact Hawaii Statewide GIS Program, Office of Planning and Sustainable Development, State of Hawaii; PO Box 2359, Honolulu, HI 96804; (808) 587-2846; email: gis@hawaii.gov; Website: https://planning.hawaii.gov/gis.NOTE: This layer is maintained by the C&C of Honolulu HOLIS. It is provided on the State of Hawaii GIS ArcGIS Online and downloading sites as a service to the public. Data is downloaded from the C&C website periodically. To obtain the latest version of the Oahu Street Centerline layer, users should visit the HOLIS Open Geospatial Data Portal at https://honolulu-cchnl.opendata.arcgis.com/.
